{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","symbolKind":"case","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"code":[" If a text's language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out vertically."],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"abstract":[{"text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingMode","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical","abstract":[],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","role":"symbol","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre"}}}